            <p class="ddp-left-title">Vector Search Use Cases</p>
            <p class="ddp-left-description">MongoDB Atlas integrates operational and vector databases in a single, unified platform. Use vector representations of your data to perform semantic search, build recommendation engines, design Q&amp;A systems, detect anomalies, or provide context for gen AI Apps.</p>
